@startuml
title Public Repository Context

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor Operator
component "scripts/\npublic launch surface" as Scripts
component "scripts/sessions/\nsession profiles" as Profiles
component "runtime output bundle\n(local operator workspace)" as RuntimeBundle
database "datasets/\ncurated measured bundles" as Datasets
component "datasets/manifest.json\npublication index" as Manifest
component "docs/\npublic repository docs" as Docs

Operator --> Scripts : launch a reference session
Scripts --> Profiles : load blocks and env template
Scripts --> RuntimeBundle : write new capture bundle
Docs --> Scripts : describe usage and boundaries
Docs --> Datasets : document publication rules
Manifest --> Datasets : index curated bundles

note right of Scripts
Reference implementation only.
No full 802.11bf or EasyMesh compliance claim.
end note

note bottom of Datasets
Published bundles keep raw/public-safe surfaces only.
Derived analysis is excluded.
end note

@enduml
